<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "S6JB0B6306017" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "1">
<title>
P&#x002F;S Pump Removal and Installation
</title>
<servinfosub id = "S6JB0B6306017001">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Be sure to clean each joint of suction and discharge sides thoroughly before removal.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect negative (&#8211;) cable at battery.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Take out P&#x002F;S fluid in reservoir with syringe or such.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect high pressure pipe and suction hose from power steering pump.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
As fluid flows out of disconnected joints, put a receptacle under joints or a plug to pipe.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect pressure switch lead wire at switch terminal.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove P&#x002F;S drive belt referring to 
<intxref refid = "S6JB0B6306006">P&#x002F;S Pump and A&#x002F;C Compressor (If Equipped) Drive Belt Removal and Installation</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove P&#x002F;S pump mounting bolts (1) and then remove P&#x002F;S pump.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove P&#x002F;S pump (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5JB0C630005.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.861mm" ver = "01" gw = "137" gh = "130"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1" align = "left">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "3.150in"/>
<tbody valign = "top">
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
P&#x002F;S pump bracket
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Plug each port of removed pump to prevent dust or any other foreign matter from entering.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<c-change/>
<servinfosub id = "S6JB0B6306017002">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "S6JB0B6306020">P&#x002F;S Pump Inspection</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Reverse removal procedure, and then nothing the following instructions.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Adjust P&#x002F;S pump drive belt referring to 
<intxref refid = "S6JB0B6306005">P&#x002F;S Pump and A&#x002F;C Compressor (If Equipped) Drive Belt Inspection and Adjustment</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Fill specified power steering fluid after installation and bleed air without failure referring to 
<intxref refid = "S6JB0B6306004">P&#x002F;S System Air Bleeding Procedure</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<torque>
